{"tid":602520,"cid":17,"subCid":0,"title":"（非回帶）入台證問題","createTime":"2018-03-23T05:19:37.000Z","updateTime":"2018-03-23T06:36:50.000Z","uid":44822,"like":0,"dislike":14,"uniUserReply":20,"replies":[{"pid":"f778cd919a44ea8df90783c0db772601f0a3921c","tid":602520,"uid":44822,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-03-23T05:19:37.000Z","msg":"Sorry各位巴打，非回帶<br />\n各位巴打屌得細力啲<br />\n我知道我準備唔夠<br />\n但希望可以盡力補救<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<br />\n我前日先網上申請入台證<br />\n佢話五個工作天內<br />\n<br />\n我下星期二去台灣<br />\n由琴日開始計得返3工作天<br />\n上網見唔少巴打話兩日內都搞到<br />\n同埋打過去台灣辨事處會唔會有機快少少"},{"pid":"1408f390927869f27b5c0af69f98b23274fe4d4d","tid":602520,"uid":21423,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-03-23T05:21:08.000Z","msg":"此回覆已被刪除"},{"pid":"f016105c0e3f741aeb72855fb9fb95bfd65624db","tid":602520,"uid":78143,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-03-23T05:22:23.000Z","msg":"香港出世<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/wonder2.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"233b9cad5c64b76e464ce188b71c124080bd10a3","tid":602520,"uid":44822,"like":0,"dislike":2,"score":-2,"quote":{"pid":"1408f390927869f27b5c0af69f98b23274fe4d4d","tid":602520,"uid":21423,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-03-23T05:21:08.000Z","msg":"此回覆已被刪除"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-03-23T05:23:48.000Z","msg":"Sorry更正<br />\n<span style=\"color: red;\">台北經濟文化辦事處</span>"},{"pid":"b10f2e326affe0e75f5a8e51b064e97c01ef4c71","tid":602520,"uid":30604,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-03-23T05:24:10.000Z","msg":"香港出世一禁就有架喇喎<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"3e1a44e45f9bd4a9f9669403566b1e2ed2c9364c","tid":602520,"uid":36696,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-03-23T05:24:34.000Z","msg":"香港出世5分鐘搞掂"},{"pid":"a88011102b2f3b9ba367580728ade5cb6668a192","tid":602520,"uid":5793,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018